Remember that incredible book idea you play around with sometimes in your head? It’s time to start writing it. This book will help get you started.

I couldn’t wait to release this book. I knew I had to get it to you. And because I just know in my gut this might be the very book you need to help your dreams come true, I’ve actually made some massive forward steps to get it to you even sooner.

On Wednesday, March 15th, you’ll be able to get your hands on A Creative Rebel’s Guide to Writing Amazing Fiction.

Where? MeghanMarchMerch.com 

I am so freaking excited about this book that I’m releasing the ebook and the audiobook almost two weeks early on my own website! 

Don’t worry, if you preordered it on your preferred retailer, it will still deliver on March 28th as planned, but if you want to get your hands on it even sooner, it will be READY TO ROCK on Wednesday, March 15th! If you want to cancel your preorder before you purchase it from meghanmarchmerch.com, you can totally do that too.

#marchmagic #meghanmarchbooks #creativerebels #newrelease #meghanmarch #binge #writing #booksonwriting

In case you missed my newsletter announcement this morning... 

I created my own happily ever after space on the internet!

And now you get to join me in my brand new digital world that is 100% positive, uplifting, encouraging, inspiring, and amazing. This is a safe haven for those who believe in happily ever afters and becoming their own hero. This is a place where we can share our wins and know that everyone is going to cheer and encourage you every step of the way, no matter where you are on your journey. This is a place where we can all be ourselves and be loved for who we are, not torn down, belittled, and told we’re not allowed to be our own uniquely beautiful souls in their full glory. That is the past. Rebels + Runaways is the future. 

I couldn’t be more excited to open the doors on Wednesday, March 15—and give you a front-row seat for the launch of this beautiful new digital haven! 

FOR YEARS, I’ve been wanting to build my own world, and after a ton of work, that dream is becoming reality. 

Stay tuned and get excited, because very soon we will all finally have a beautiful space where we can celebrate and be inspired together!!!

#meghanmarch #rebelsandrunaways #meghanmarchbooks #creativerebel #RR #happilyeverafter #inspire #uplift

Today is the day!!! I have TWO huge launches happening TODAY!!! WOOOHOOO!! 

First, my newest book, A Creative Rebel’s Guide To Writing Amazing Fiction is out.

I put my heart and soul into this book in hopes that it would serve many on their creative journeys. I hope it helps you make all of your dreams come true. You never know what incredible changes can happen in your life when you learn to write amazing fiction! 

AND…. my next super exciting announcement!!! My brand new community is LIVE!! We’ve thrown open the doors and we cannot wait to welcome you into Rebels + Runaways! 

This is a 100% positive, supportive, uplifting community for Runaway Readers and Creative Rebels. This is where you will find ME, all of my exclusive content, wonderful like-minded friends, awesome discussions, and more! Also, you can join my inner circle and become a Meghan March Superfan and get even more of ME and my never before seen videos and behind-the-scenes action!

Helping other people's dreams become reality? That's my jam!

If you haven't heard the story yet, I had been thinking of writing a children's book for a while - but it wasn't until @joshwoods shared his childhood dream of illustrating one that I thought...

"We have to make this happen!"

Then it hit me. What if we wrote about his hairless cat Beatrice? The words came right into my mind & that was it! 

BEATRICE was born!

Sometimes, you have to go with your heart. You have to support other people's dreams & do everything you can to make them a reality! 

After all, you always end up blessed!

What I love most about my husband:
-He's a truth teller. Even if it hurts, it's because he truly cares and wants what's best for people.
-He protects. He's fiercely protective of those he loves.
-He works hard. He is diligent. He will see a project through to the end.
-He is creative. Some of the biggest plot points in my books come from him!
-He is beautiful. Inside & out! Of course, he is living art & crazy handsome, but he's just as beautiful inside! 🥰🥰

My books used to take over my life. I worked tirelessly.

1,000 words a day. 5,000 words a day. 10,000 words a day. 20,000 words a day! I became imprisoned by it.

It took me taking a step back from writing altogether to truly find myself and understand that:

I can write however I want to!

Redemption has been a beautiful process. I have written when I want to; when I feel inspired!

I have been patient with myself and the process ❤️

It has been the RIGHT way for me in this space.

What can YOU adjust that will be the right way for you?
#workhappy #meghanmarch #enjoythejourney #loveyourselfmore #redemption #redemptioniscoming #meghanmarchbooks

Saints & Sinners
The Rome Hennessy Story

Synopsis:

“The moment I met her, I knew she was different.” - Rome Hennessy

Black Ops Boogeyman Rome Hennessy never expected to meet “the one.” After spending decades in warm climates being shot at and shooting back with bigger guns, he never thought that kind of lightning would strike for him. When it does, in a snow globe of a town full of rednecks and bikers in the mountains of BFE Idaho, the man who is always ready for anything learns he isn’t ready for this. Life, as he knows it, will never be the same. 

God Bless America.

Big Daddy Rome is coming home to stay.

I took a break from writing.

I literally couldn't write another book. I had already written 12 more books than I should have without taking a break.

And my creativity has burst forward again ... trust me, I'm not stopping anytime soon!
